import {React,useState} from 'react' export default function ProductDetails(props) { const [count, setCount] = useState(1); const details = props.details; const Check = () => { if(count<=1) return; else setCount(count-1) }; return (

{details.category}

{details.title}

{details.description}

Quantity {count}
${details.price} { /* */ }
) }
